565
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:34,760
This Physician Dou comes from the Courtyard of Misfortune.

566
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:37,290
If he wins, we seamstresses of the Bureau of Imperial Attire,

567
00:42:37,290 --> 00:42:40,240
